description:
Get everything your baby needs in just 1-2 days! Plus, FREE shipping on orders $49+. If only every delivery were this easy.
 
Diapers.com is the fast, easy (and fun!) way to get everything your baby needs delivered at lightning speed. No crowds, no empty shelves, no bundling up baby. Diapers, wipes, formula, clothing & more, delivered in 1-2 days!*
 
“A must-have app for every mom!”– Aspen_mom_35
“Great app! Life saver!” – Meghixs
“So easy! I can order stuff while I’m holding the baby.” – NewMommy36
“Perfect for new parents.”– Portense
 
Here’s what you’ll love:
 
•SHOP ANYWHERE, ANYTIME: Whether you’re on the go, or on the couch. 
•FIND STUFF FAST: Shop for diapers, wipes, formula, clothing & more in seconds. 
•SCAN IT, SEARCH IT: Scan any barcode, from any store, to find that item on Diapers.com. 
•BABY REGISTRY: Create and manage your baby registry straight from the app. Add and remove items, see what’s been purchased (by who), and share a link to your registry by email. 
•SEE THE BIG PICTURE: View baby stuff in all its glory. Big, beautiful images show you every detail. 
•10 SITES, 1 CART: Get everything you need in one order from our Familyhood sites: Diapers.com, Soap.com, Wag.com, YoYo.com, BeautyBar.com, Casa.com, VineMarket.com, AfterSchool.com, Bookworm.com, and Look.com. 
•EASY REORDER: Quickly reorder anything you’ve purchased in the past (from any of our sites). 
•PRODUCT REVIEWS: Don’t just take our word for it. Find out what other customers think before you buy.
 
*Delivery may take more than 2 days for certain products or for orders placed on Friday or Saturday. Please see product detail pages for estimated delivery times. No delivery on Sunday or major holidays.
releaseNotes:
4.4.1:
• Fix to Touch ID authentication. Some users may have seen extra Touch ID prompts after upgrading. Sorry about that!

4.4:
• Proper support for iOS 8, iPhone 6, and iPhone 6 Plus.
• Touch ID-enabled users can checkout with a fingerprint instead of a password.
• Manage your email contact preferences.
• As always: plenty of bug fixes and performance improvements.
